\n9k一個月<br />\n做緊自己鍾意既嘢<br />\n依家好開心<br />\n<br />\nps：接近40歲"},{"pid":"05502abc9a8a1e466c6ebc5192887544e4e2141c","tid":564440,"uid":106506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:26:35.000Z","msg":"所以話真係"},{"pid":"0e2abb9a2f48c1e2e18c08cccf5ed577d284d6b9","tid":564440,"uid":17781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T02:07:54.000Z","msg":"Agger，窮做咩都係錯，做咩都要比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b816617afcd8996d0c9d5eb00375ffa2ef0dff9","tid":564440,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T02:08:39.000Z","msg":"well. you  are 岩"},{"pid":"a0641f6b5e854c2d6b04633ef77455dcd2cb921f","tid":564440,"uid":154768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:14:58.000Z","msg":"你成段野 只係話人地話你點點點<br />\n你話窮做咩都錯 係個社會 係其他人話你錯<br />\n但睇你意思 如果你自己都覺得自己錯 咁你咪真係錯<br />\n成日話窮就點點點 叫佢去搵野學下又話冇錢<br />\n學樣興趣 一個月千幾蚊好未 都唔願意去 <br />\n如果你話冇興趣咁冇問題 你話冇錢？<br />\n根本係個思考模式有問題 連自己都唔願活出自我 <br />\n憑咩怨天怨地"},{"pid":"51d98827306795e4249deab2733581bd2473fb6c","tid":564440,"uid":72489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:20:43.000Z","msg":"咁care人地點睇你，<br />\n<br />\n注定一世發唔到圍。"},{"pid":"660ecaf053dba9c30a64670a26e1c41e244a0855","tid":564440,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"人地講乜你要聽<br />\n<br />\n聽完發覺係歪理根本唔洗理"}]}